Package: gramr
Title: The Grammar of Grammar
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(person("Jasmine", "Dumas", email = "jasmine.dumas@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")), 
             person("Ben", "Marwick", email = "benamrwick@gmail.com", role = "aut"),
             person("Gordon", "Shotwell", email = "g.e.shotwell@gmail.com", role = "aut"))
Description: Checks for grammar and spelling and avoids some obvious 
    programming nomenclature such as hex codes, existing package names, and file extensions.
